with Sal.

242
00:10:48.398 --> 00:10:50.817
There woulda never been shit
with Sal if it wasn't for you.

243
00:10:50.984 --> 00:10:52.986
You brought that cocksucker
over the river.

244
00:10:53.153 --> 00:10:55.072
