287
00:13:12.584 --> 00:13:14.103
What y'all been hearin'
about this nigga 'Nique?

288
00:13:14.127 --> 00:13:15.128
Where he at?

289
00:13:15.295 --> 00:13:16.575
All I'm hearing
is he on the run.

290
00:13:17.422 --> 00:13:19.466
Nah. I hear he hidin' out
