about your daughter.

358
00:16:33.201 --> 00:16:34.201
Iesha.

359
00:16:35.370 --> 00:16:37.706
[dramatic musical transition]

360
00:16:39.666 --> 00:16:42.544
These mafia niggas run Manhattan
just like they run Queens.

361
00:16:42.711 --> 00:16:43.920
Different ones.

362
00:16:44.087 --> 00:16:45.672
And nobody know more than us
these dagos

363
00:16:45.839 --> 00:16:47.924
like nothing better
than to fuck with each other.

364
00:16:48.091 --> 00:16:49.718
All that honor
and integrity bullshit

365
00:16:49.884 --> 00:16:51.219
go right out the fuckin' window

366
00:16:51.344 --> 00:16:52.697
