I'm there every day ♪</i>

448
00:21:10.019 --> 00:21:11.479
<i>♪ To love you ♪</i>

449
00:21:12.105 --> 00:21:14.273
[backing vocalist]
<i>♪ To love you ♪</i>

450
00:21:14.399 --> 00:21:15.775
<i>♪ Hold you ♪</i>

451
00:21:16.401 --> 00:21:18.695
[backing vocalist] <i>♪ Hold you ♪</i>

452
00:21:18.861 --> 00:21:21.864
<i>♪ Kissin' all over
Your body. bae ♪</i>

453
00:21:22.031 --> 00:21:23.574
[backing vocalist]
<i>♪ Body. baby ♪</i>

454
00:21:23.741 --> 00:21:26.577
<i>♪ This the type of love
You need every day ♪</i>

455
00:21:26.744 --> 00:21:28.162
<i>♪ I told you ♪</i>

456
00:21:30.039 --> 00:21:32.542
<i>♪ There's no one better ♪</i>

457
00:21:33.126 --> 00:21:34.627
